             was indicted for <rs id="t18150215-103-off615" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18150215-103-off615" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18150215-103-off615" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18150215-103-cd616" type="crimeDate">16th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150215-103-off615 t18150215-103-cd616"></join>, in the dwelling-house of 
                     <persName id="t18150215-103-person867">
                        Mary 
                        Shallhorn
                     <interp inst="t18150215-103-person867" type="surname" value="Shallhorn"></interp>
